    {
        "content": "<p>It seems to be <code>AddCommGroup.sub_modEq_zero</code>. I think you either need to write out the full name with the namespace or put <code>open AddCommGroup</code> somewhere above your definition</p>",
        "id": 472756659,
        "sender_full_name": "Niels Voss",
        "timestamp": 1727290370
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=AddCommGroup.sub_modEq_zero#doc\">docs#AddCommGroup.sub_modEq_zero</a></p>",
        "id": 472756756,
        "sender_full_name": "Niels Voss",
        "timestamp": 1727290438
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>This works:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Algebra</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ModEq</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℤ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≡</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">PMOD</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">6</span><span class=\"o\">])</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≡</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">PMOD</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">6</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">AddCommGroup</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sub_modEq_zero</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mpr</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h0</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
